<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: aggressive heat dump -->
  <VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.label>攻性熵轉移</VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.label>
  <!-- EN: Instantly dump all of your neural heat into a target, causing them to explode with an area of effect relative to the heat lost and the target’s psychic sensitivity. A good declaration of war. -->
  <VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.description>立刻把你的所有心靈熵都傾注到目標身上，目標會產生一次爆炸，範圍取決於你轉移的心靈熵。十分兇猛的戰爭行為。</VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 攻性熵轉移 -->
  <VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.verbProperties.label>攻擊性熵轉移</VPE_AggressiveHeatDump.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: berserk -->
  <VPE_Berserk.label>激怒</VPE_Berserk.label>
  <!-- EN: Induce a berserker psychosis in the target's mind, causing them to attack anyone nearby. They regain rationality after 15 seconds, depending on their psychic sensitivity. -->
  <VPE_Berserk.description>將一個怒不可遏的想法植入到目標心裡，這會讓他們嘗試攻擊附近任何人。目標在至少15秒後會恢復正常，具體時間取決於目標的心靈敏感度。</VPE_Berserk.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Berserk.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Berserk.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 激怒 -->
  <VPE_Berserk.verbProperties.label>激怒</VPE_Berserk.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: berskerk pulse -->
  <VPE_BerserkPulse.label>狂暴脈衝</VPE_BerserkPulse.label>
  <!-- EN: Generate an overwhelming rush of undirected rage in everyone near the target point. Considered an overt act of aggression and lasts several seconds. -->
  <VPE_BerserkPulse.description>在目標點周圍的每個人身上產生一股無法抑制的狂怒。使用該能力是公開的侵略行為，會持續數秒。</VPE_BerserkPulse.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_BerserkPulse.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_BerserkPulse.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 狂暴脈衝 -->
  <VPE_BerserkPulse.verbProperties.label>狂暴脈衝</VPE_BerserkPulse.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: burden -->
  <VPE_Burden.label>重負</VPE_Burden.label>
  <!-- EN: Slow the target for a short time by suppressing motor activity in the brain. Considered a hostile action and affected by the target’s psychic sensitivity. -->
  <VPE_Burden.description>通過抑制大腦的運動中樞，在短時間內減慢目標的行動能力。被視作敵對行為，效果取決於目標的心靈敏感度。</VPE_Burden.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Burden.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Burden.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 重負 -->
  <VPE_Burden.verbProperties.label>重負</VPE_Burden.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: neural heat detonation -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.label>心熵爆破</VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.label>
  <!-- EN: Efficiently but indiscriminately dumps all of the caster’s neural heat into an explosion away from themselves, the size being both relative to the heat lost and their psychic sensitivity. -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.description>將施放者所有的心靈熵轉移到遠處並引發爆炸，範圍取決於你轉移的心靈熵。</VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 心熵爆破 -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.verbProperties.label>心熵爆破</VPE_NeuralHeatDetonation.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: neural heat dump -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDump.label>熵轉移</VPE_NeuralHeatDump.label>
  <!-- EN: Instantly dump all your neural heat into a conscious ally. As a side effect, the target will fall into a debilitating, harmless coma for about a day. The target must actively accept the psychic invasion, so only conscious allies can be targeted. -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDump.description>立刻把你的所有心靈熵都傾注到一個友方目標身上。作為副作用，目標會陷入一個大約持續一天的昏迷中。目標必須主動接受精神入侵，所以只有清醒的盟友才能成為目標。</VPE_NeuralHeatDump.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDump.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_NeuralHeatDump.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 熵轉移 -->
  <VPE_NeuralHeatDump.verbProperties.label>熵轉移</VPE_NeuralHeatDump.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: neuroquake -->
  <VPE_Neuroquake.label>神經震顫</VPE_Neuroquake.label>
  <!-- EN: Find a discontinuity in the psychic field and unfold it, releasing a massive amount of psychic energy. Every creature in range but outside of the safe inner circle will be driven violently insane. Casting this takes 12 seconds of meditation, and afterwards, the caster will go into a five-day psychic coma. The disturbing neuroquake echoes will inflict pain on everyone for many kilometers around, causing diplomatic consequences with all factions. -->
  <VPE_Neuroquake.description>展開精神域場中不連續的地方，釋放出大量的精神能量。在安全的內圈之外的每一個生物都會被猛烈的心靈脈衝逼瘋。施放這個能力需要12秒的冥想，之後，施放者將進入五天的精神昏迷。令人不安的神經震盪回聲將給周圍數公里內的人帶來痛苦，並且對所有派系產生外交影響。</VPE_Neuroquake.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Neuroquake.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Neuroquake.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: If you use neuroquake, everyone in this region will feel the neuroquake echo, you will lose goodwill with every non-hostile faction.\n\nNeuroquake takes 12 seconds to cast, and cannot be interrupted. When complete, the caster will fall into a psychic coma for 5 days.\n\nEveryone in range except those in a small circle around the caster will be affected.\n\nDo you really want to cast neuroquake? -->
  <VPE_Neuroquake.modExtensions.0.message>如果你使用神經震顫，這個地區的所有人都會感受到「神經震顫」的迴響，你將失去與所有非敵對派系的部分好感。\n\n神經震顫需要12秒的釋放時間，並且不能被打斷。完成後，施放者也會進入心靈休克數天。\n\n地圖上除了施放者周圍一個小範圍的人之外，其他人都會受到影響。\n\n你真的要釋放神經震顫嗎？</VPE_Neuroquake.modExtensions.0.message>
  <!-- EN: 神經震顫 -->
  <VPE_Neuroquake.verbProperties.label>神經震顫</VPE_Neuroquake.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic drone -->
  <VPE_PsychicDrone.label>心靈噪音</VPE_PsychicDrone.label>
  <!-- EN: Creates a massive psychic drone aura around the caster tuned to hostiles, frequently driving them insane until they overcome the break. Duration scales with the caster’s psychic sensitivity. -->
  <VPE_PsychicDrone.description>在施放者的周圍構建一個心靈噪音的光環，範圍內的所有敵方單位會持續受到精神上的壓力直到他們精神崩潰。持續時間取決於施放者的心靈敏感度。</VPE_PsychicDrone.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_PsychicDrone.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_PsychicDrone.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 心靈噪音 -->
  <VPE_PsychicDrone.verbProperties.label>心靈噪音</VPE_PsychicDrone.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: psychic shock -->
  <VPE_PsychicShock.label>心靈衝擊</VPE_PsychicShock.label>
  <!-- EN: Psychically shocks the target's mind with chaotic images, blocking coherent perception and dropping them into a state of psychic shock. There is a risk of brain damage and is overtly hostile. -->
  <VPE_PsychicShock.description>用混亂的影像衝擊目標的大腦，擾亂其感知，使其進入心靈衝擊狀態一段時間。有很高几率導致大腦損傷。</VPE_PsychicShock.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_PsychicShock.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_PsychicShock.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 心靈衝擊 -->
  <VPE_PsychicShock.verbProperties.label>心靈衝擊</VPE_PsychicShock.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: stun -->
  <VPE_Stun.label>麻痹</VPE_Stun.label>
  <!-- EN: Momentarily disrupts motor function in the target's brain, preventing any movement. This lasts for a few seconds and is considered a hostile action. -->
  <VPE_Stun.description>瞬間擾亂目標大腦的運動中樞，使其麻痹無法行動。</VPE_Stun.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Stun.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Stun.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 麻痹 -->
  <VPE_Stun.verbProperties.label>麻痹</VPE_Stun.verbProperties.label>
  
